attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes & Gardens - Wine Country Group

data.description: Move into this beautiful 2006 energy-efficient 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom custom home today!  New interior paint throughout. Dual-pane windows for energy efficiency. Durable high-quality Pergo laminate flooring throughout.  Large living room with propane fireplace, high ceilings, and sliding glass door to the backyard. All bedrooms on the main level. Spacious downstairs room that could be a game room, media room, guest bedroom, or whatever you need it to be Kitchen with a nice box window by the sink, white tile counters, backsplash, and breakfast bar and all electric appliances. Spacious back deck with a nice view of Mount Konocti. Large master bedroom with sliding glass door to the back deck. Large master bathroom with walk-in closet, dual sinks, and shower. This home is move-in ready and has everything you need to relax and entertain. The large living room is perfect for hosting family gatherings or watching a movie with friends. The kitchen is spacious and well-equipped, making it easy to whip up delicious meals. The backyard is the perfect place to relax and enjoy the outdoors. And the master bedroom is the perfect place to unwind after a long day. It's the perfect place to raise a family or enjoy your retirement. Schedule a showing today!
